body:
I tried to build TF 1.6 with `bazel -c dbg` on OSX 10.11.6, but failed with the attached error :-(

```bash
bazel build -c dbg //tensorflow/tools/pip_package:build_pip_package
```

[error.log](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/1823183/error.log)

using another box with the same OS X 10.11.6 to build TF with bazel 0.5.4 ended with errors too, although it is different from the above one.

[error.log](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/1827816/error.log)
